00:48:51,000 --> 00:48:53,000
[SPEAKER_00] Upravo obrana izaziva ti stres.

804
00:48:53,000 --> 00:48:54,000
[SPEAKER_00] Znaš kad je neko defanzivan.

805
00:48:54,000 --> 00:48:59,000
